data.description: Fabulous 2 story home with sparkling pool features 4 large bedrooms, 2 living areas, 2 dining areas, warm designer colors, 2 fireplaces, ceramic wet areas, spacious master retreat & includes a ton of energy efficient bonuses such as a radiant barrier, double pane storm windows, solar screens, insulated garage doors, new roof 2016, 5 ton AC unit, flagstone patio in backyard & so much more!
data.whatILove: This home has been upgraded to be very energy efficient. The patio and pool area have been renovated, making them an excellent place to relax or entertain. No other home in the area has as many upgrades to the outdoor space. The neighborhood was listed by the Dallas Morning News as one of the 10 safest in the metroplex.
